name: DeKalb
absentee_method: Released with cumulative results periodically election night
poll_display_race: Polls close at 7 p.m. Eastern time.
expectations_text_race: A small number of absentee, provisional and overseas military ballots remain uncounted. The secretary of state said Friday that because of the small margin between the presidential candidates, there will be a recount.
